mention.text: SEOUL , South Korea -LRB- AP -RRB- __ N Two major South Korean labor groups rallied about 15,000 workers in central Seoul on Sunday to protest government
the first such joint rally in three years for the Federation of Korean Trade Unions and the militant Korean Confederation of Trade Unions
Two major South Korean labor groups
The protesters , many carrying signs or wearing red headbands and vests with slogans such as `` Fight '' and `` Solidarity '' printed on them , chanted and pumped their fists in the air .
